Skills.Name: F.S.C.
Skills.Description: Grants 2x "Mystic Power" on all allies for 25s. Also raises Healing Boost by <color=red>{2}%</color> for 20s. Further raises SP Boost Rate by {3}% for 20s if Blue Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Grants "Mystic Power", raises Healing Boost of all allies, raises SP Boost Rate if Blue Elemental

Skills.Name: Electronic Repair
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of single ally with lowest HP by <color=red>{0}%</color> of ATK. Raises DEF of all Blue Elemental allies by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 15s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP of single ally. Raises DEF of all Blue Elemental allies

Skills.Name: Press Here
Skills.Description: Raises own Overheal based on total "Mystic Power" (Stacked) on all characters in battle multiplied by {1}% (Permanent). Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>{3}%</color> of ATK.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises own Overheal based on total "Mystic Power" in battle. Recovers HP of all allies

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>5.00%-50.00%</color> according to Combo Bonus. Inflicts 100.00% DMG.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP of all allies. Inflicts DMG on single enemy

Skills.Name: Laid-back Rebel
Skills.Description: Every 7s after start of Wave, inflicts Slow on all enemies for 5s. Also inflicts Dark for 5s. Further raises DMG Received based on total "Mystic Power" (Stacked) on all characters in battle multiplied by <color=red>{3}%</color> for 5s. Raises ATK of all allies based on total "Mystic Power" (Stacked) on all characters in battle multiplied by {6}% for 10s. Further raises DEF based on total "Mystic Power" (Stacked) on all characters in battle multiplied by {9}% for 10s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Every 7s after start of Wave, inflicts Slow and Dark on all enemies, raises DMG Received based on total "Mystic Power" in battle. Raises ATK and DEF of all allies based on total "Mystic Power" in battle
